description: There’s way more to Oahu than Waikiki or Honolulu, and this candid guidebook covers it all. Discover roaring waterfalls, quiet beaches, colourful reefs, and decent places to eat after exploring trails and valleys. Every restaurant, activity provider and place to stay is reviewed personally and anonymously by the authors.
